        Returns:

      • checkChangeTempPermission

        public boolean checkChangeTempPermission​(int x,
                                         int y)
        Checks if a user has permission to change the temperature of a certain room.
        Parameters:
        x - The x coordinate of the room the user is trying to modify.
        y - The y coordinate of the room the user is trying to modify.
        Returns:
        boolean true if the user is allowed to modify room temperature or false if not.

      • verifyCurrentUserSHHPermission

        public void verifyCurrentUserSHHPermission()
        Verifies if the user has permission to modify and access SHH. If the user has permission, the panel is accessible, if the user does not have permission, the panel is disabled.

      • disableSHHPanel

        public void disableSHHPanel​(boolean bool)
        Disables or make the SHH panel available.
        Parameters:
        bool - true, the panel will be disabled except for the temperature override. false, the panel will not be disabled.
